bosses.title: Ed the Scourge
bosses.lore: Before sliced bread, Ed was Scourging, before water was wet, Ed was Scourging, before the creation of these Forsaken Lands, Ed was Scourging

bosses.title: Zullie, Witch of the West
bosses.lore: Once a simple scholar in pursuit of the knowledge of Chaos Sorcery, found herself overcome with Hot Cheeto Fury, as Chaos was always Cheetos....

bosses.title: BradBrandt
bosses.lore: Brad was actually my kitchen knife turned into a sacred Relic, he's still really good at cutting bread
